210
00:14:57,320 --> 00:14:59,760
So I tried talking
with the restaurant’s manager,

211
00:14:59,760 --> 00:15:01,840
and he told me the price.

212
00:15:02,240 --> 00:15:04,240
But it’s so expensive.
I can’t afford it.

213
00:15:04,680 --> 00:15:05,820
But he said

214
00:15:05,900 --> 00:15:07,680
he would go talk to the owner about it.

215
00:15:07,680 --> 00:15:09,680
So the owner made an appointment
with me, here,

216
00:15:09,680 --> 00:15:10,600
today.

217
00:15:10,600 --> 00:15:14,560
So I invited you all here
to talk about it.

218
00:15:17,080 --> 00:15:18,640
Did you secretly install a tracker
on her?

219
00:15:19,080 --> 00:15:20,520
I see you following her everywhere.

220
00:15:30,680 --> 00:15:31,920
Not this time.

221
00:15:32,640 --> 00:15:35,360
Because this time,
I was the one who invited her.

222
00:15:36,440 --> 00:15:37,480
Huh?

223
00:15:38,360 --> 00:15:40,200
