00:19:19,880 --> 00:19:21,720
Then the girl will see a meteor
from that direction.

283
00:19:21,880 --> 00:19:24,360
She’ll be in shock
and will quickly grab his hands.

284
00:19:24,360 --> 00:19:25,400
Just like this.

285
00:19:25,400 --> 00:19:28,760
