287
00:19:33,280 --> 00:19:36,040
I wish to be with you forever.

288
00:19:37,160 --> 00:19:38,560
Like this, alright?

289
00:19:38,640 --> 00:19:39,280
Okay.

290
00:19:39,280 --> 00:19:40,280
Hold on.

291
00:19:40,720 --> 00:19:41,960
Can you repeat that again?

292
00:19:42,640 --> 00:19:43,840
I’m just feeling it.

293
00:19:45,040 --> 00:19:46,840
Hey, stop playing.

294
00:19:46,840 --> 00:19:48,160
Everyone, be in set up position.

295
00:19:48,160 --> 00:19:49,640
Everyone, get ready.

296
00:19:54,120 --> 00:19:55,040
Let’s go.

297
00:19:55,320 --> 00:19:56,320
Camera.

298
00:19:56,320 --> 00:19:57,160
Speed.

299
00:19:57,440 --> 00:19:59,360
And action.

300
00:20:00,440 --> 00:20:01,480
A meteor.

301
00:20:02,760 --> 00:20:03,720
Um.

302
00:20:10,760 --> 00:20:12,240
What did you wish for?

303
00:20:13,560 --> 00:20:15,760
I wish to be with you forever.

304
00:20:18,840 --> 00:20:20,600
I’ll be right beside you.

305
00:20:26,000 --> 00:20:27,000
Cut.

306
00:20:27,000 --> 00:20:28,800
Great job. This was great.

307
00:20:32,800 --> 00:20:33,960
