314
00:20:45,480 --> 00:20:46,240
Huh?

315
00:20:46,880 --> 00:20:47,880
Just a hug?

316
00:20:47,880 --> 00:20:48,840
Yes.

317
00:20:48,840 --> 00:20:49,960
Nonsense.

318
00:20:51,480 --> 00:20:52,960
It came out great.

319
00:20:53,280 --> 00:20:55,240
