the camera angle.

320
00:20:56,960 --> 00:20:57,640
Hey.

321
00:20:57,840 --> 00:21:00,800
Both leading roles don’t seem to have
any problems.

322
00:21:01,120 --> 00:21:02,560
It’s boring.

323
00:21:02,560 --> 00:21:03,560
It’s not interesting.

324
00:21:03,560 --> 00:21:05,000
Also

325
00:21:05,280 --> 00:21:07,120
many memories of love stories

326
