327
00:21:10,080 --> 00:21:11,920
That’s why it’s more memorable
for the audience.

328
00:21:14,600 --> 00:21:15,320
No.

329
00:21:15,560 --> 00:21:16,900
I want it to be

330
00:21:16,900 --> 00:21:18,040
a moment of comfort.

331
00:21:18,120 --> 00:21:21,840
A couple being together
is a great memory.

332
00:21:23,280 --> 00:21:25,000
Long distance relationships
don’t work out.

333
00:21:27,600 --> 00:21:29,560
Alright, everyone,
get ready for the next scene.

334
00:21:29,560 --> 00:21:31,000
All ready.

335
00:21:31,000 --> 00:21:32,520
Starting from not answering calls,

336
00:21:33,840 --> 00:21:35,480
saying I’m busy as an excuse.

337
00:21:36,280 --> 00:21:38,520
Then later on, having weird behaviors

338
00:21:38,520 --> 00:21:40,800
