339
00:21:41,880 --> 00:21:44,120
Do you want to continue the shoot?

340
00:21:45,520 --> 00:21:47,520
Alright, everyone be ready.

341
00:21:58,680 --> 00:22:00,360
And action.

342
00:22:07,880 --> 00:22:09,840
Pai, I’m going to go now.

343
00:22:10,160 --> 00:22:11,480
Um.

344
00:22:12,240 --> 00:22:13,240
This...

345
00:22:14,600 --> 00:22:15,640
Oh this...

346
00:22:15,640 --> 00:22:17,360
This is a project from work.

347
00:22:17,360 --> 00:22:20,600
I hired Ta as a freelance photographer.

348
00:22:21,240 --> 00:22:23,040
He just sent me the work to approve.

349
00:22:23,360 --> 00:22:25,600
But his skill is great, isn’t it?

350
00:22:30,600 --> 00:22:32,680
The script you wrote,

351
00:22:32,680 --> 00:22:34,440
it’s about you and Pupaa, right?

352
00:22:35,520 --> 00:22:37,720
You miss him so much
so you had to turn it into a short film?

353
00:22:38,360 --> 00:22:39,520
So romantic.

354
00:22:47,520 --> 00:22:48,400
Yes.

355
00:22:49,160 --> 00:22:50,520
I’m about to

356
00:22:52,000 --> 00:22:53,160
leave right now.

357
00:22:55,960 --> 00:22:56,920
Sure.

358
00:22:58,040 --> 00:23:00,880
Even if Ta has been having
bad reputation about all the girls,

359
00:23:00,880 --> 00:23:03,080
but I know him well.

360
00:23:03,840 --> 00:23:07,600
I can confirm to you
that he really has changed.

361
00:23:08,280 --> 00:23:10,320
Are you really not going to give him
another chance?

362
00:23:16,800 --> 00:23:18,840
Actually

