370
00:23:41,200 --> 00:23:42,320
So I...

371
00:23:42,320 --> 00:23:43,080
Is she accurate?

372
00:23:44,360 --> 00:23:45,440
Yes.

373
00:23:46,800 --> 00:23:47,560
Wawa.

374
00:23:51,680 --> 00:23:53,680
I’m about to go home.

375
00:23:56,120 --> 00:23:57,200
Are you free?

376
00:23:58,440 --> 00:23:59,720
Can you drop me off?

377
00:24:01,600 --> 00:24:02,640
I sure am.

378
00:24:03,200 --> 00:24:04,680
I’m always available for you.

379
00:24:05,720 --> 00:24:06,960
Let’s go home.

380
00:24:09,880 --> 00:24:10,760
I’ll head out now.

381
00:24:10,760 --> 00:24:11,520
Alright.

382
00:24:11,520 --> 00:24:12,640
- Bye.
- Bye.

