coming to watch it too?

395
00:27:09,880 --> 00:27:12,760
It’s just a little review.
Let’s not disturb him.

396
00:27:13,240 --> 00:27:14,840
It’s good that he’s not here.

397
00:27:15,160 --> 00:27:16,160
Let’s start it.

398
00:27:17,000 --> 00:27:17,840
Okay.

399
00:28:21,480 --> 00:28:24,120
I’ve been through so much
in terms of relationships.

400
00:28:24,640 --> 00:28:26,240
And don’t say that I’m intruding.

401
00:28:26,880 --> 00:28:30,640
Such romantic love
only happens in dreams.

402
00:28:31,400 --> 00:28:32,880
Thinking back,

403
00:28:34,000 --> 00:28:37,760
