407
00:28:56,760 --> 00:28:58,440
How did we get to this topic?

408
00:29:03,840 --> 00:29:05,560
You want to know, right?

409
00:29:05,560 --> 00:29:07,640
If you’re interested,
I’ll take you there.

410
00:29:08,560 --> 00:29:09,520
But

411
00:29:09,520 --> 00:29:11,360
it’s girls only.

412
00:29:11,560 --> 00:29:12,520
Alright.

413
00:29:23,280 --> 00:29:25,080
You’re a fortune teller too?

414
00:29:25,320 --> 00:29:26,040
Um.

415
00:29:26,040 --> 00:29:28,680
I used to be well-known in this area.

416
00:29:29,240 --> 00:29:32,520
But my sales have been rising,

417
00:29:32,520 --> 00:29:34,600
so I haven’t had the time to continue.

418
00:29:34,600 --> 00:29:36,920
But I’ll give you a special treat today.

419
00:29:37,520 --> 00:29:38,480
Sure.

420
00:29:39,120 --> 00:29:41,040
Alright, I’ll start first.

421
00:29:41,040 --> 00:29:42,080
So we know if it’s accurate or not.

422
00:29:42,360 --> 00:29:43,000
Um.

423
00:29:43,440 --> 00:29:46,600
Alright, you can start off
by choosing three cards.

424
00:30:01,200 --> 00:30:02,560
I’m going to open it now.

425
00:30:04,500 --> 00:30:07,480
(TEAMPERANCE)

426
00:30:07,480 --> 00:30:10,000
These three cards

427
00:30:10,960 --> 00:30:12,240
