428
00:30:12,800 --> 00:30:16,320
it’s an on-and-off thing going on.

429
00:30:16,520 --> 00:30:19,120
If something good happened,
you’ll have to be aware

430
00:30:19,120 --> 00:30:20,800
that something bad will follow up.

431
00:30:33,240 --> 00:30:34,280
Next.

432
00:30:35,200 --> 00:30:36,640
Pai’s turn.

433
00:30:37,760 --> 00:30:38,560
Sure.

434
00:30:42,600 --> 00:30:45,240
Alright, choose three cards.

435
00:31:07,300 --> 00:31:14,180
(FOUR OF CUPS THE DEVIL
THREE OF SWORDS)

436
00:31:19,200 --> 00:31:20,280
Well,

437
00:31:21,240 --> 00:31:23,800
you’re about to know the truth
about something.

438
00:31:25,240 --> 00:31:27,920
It’s about a third person.

439
00:31:29,880 --> 00:31:34,640
And there will be a girl from the past
involved.

440
00:31:40,720 --> 00:31:43,440
You should take it slow.

441
00:31:43,440 --> 00:31:46,560
That’s what the cards say.

442
00:31:46,840 --> 00:31:51,280
And my cards are very accurate.

443
00:31:58,920 --> 00:32:01,600
(Prapai, my friend and Pupaa
are in the same university)

444
00:32:01,600 --> 00:32:04,720
(She said that this girl
is Pupaa’s first love)

445
00:32:23,160 --> 00:32:24,440
Pai.

446
00:32:25,040 --> 00:32:28,680
This is another box
that Pupaa left for you.

447
00:32:32,080 --> 00:32:33,360
Thank you.

448
00:33:25,720 --> 00:33:28,880
(Use the magnet in the box
to stick it to the doll)

449
00:33:28,880 --> 00:33:32,320
(Then take the two dolls
and put them together)

450
00:33:32,880 --> 00:33:35,520
(And there I am, right next to you)

451
00:34:11,480 --> 00:34:12,600
This is not working.

452
00:34:12,920 --> 00:34:14,440
I have to do something.

453
00:34:20,220 --> 00:34:21,500
(FOUR OF CUPS)

454
00:34:27,980 --> 00:34:31,020
(THREE OF SWORDS)

455
00:34:33,280 --> 00:34:34,160
Oh.

456
00:34:35,680 --> 00:34:38,600
