Let me see.

457
00:34:39,420 --> 00:34:41,020
(THE WORLD)

458
00:34:41,720 --> 00:34:45,280
So then that means the prediction
will be...

459
00:34:46,840 --> 00:34:49,320
Pupaa is not cheating on her.

460
00:34:50,360 --> 00:34:51,720
Oh no.

461
00:34:52,400 --> 00:34:53,960
I have to tell Prapai.

462
00:34:55,200 --> 00:34:59,920
But if I tell her, she’ll say that
the card is not accurate.

463
00:35:00,720 --> 00:35:03,600
So then I guess I won’t tell.

464
00:35:04,440 --> 00:35:05,400
Never mind.

465
00:35:07,720 --> 00:35:09,920
