466
00:35:12,540 --> 00:35:13,860
(THE WORLD)
(THREE OF SWORDS)

467
00:35:20,920 --> 00:35:22,000
(Prapai)

468
00:35:22,000 --> 00:35:23,320
(Rejected)

469
00:35:23,320 --> 00:35:25,040
(The other party canceled the call)

470
00:35:25,040 --> 00:35:27,800
(Did you call me?)

471
00:35:28,800 --> 00:35:29,680
Pupaa.

472
00:35:30,000 --> 00:35:32,000
