494
00:36:40,360 --> 00:36:41,600
I’ll take over it.

495
00:36:42,520 --> 00:36:43,480
There’s nothing left.

496
00:36:43,480 --> 00:36:45,800
But the remaining miscellaneous tasks,

497
00:36:45,800 --> 00:36:47,600
I’ll finish them off today.

498
00:36:48,720 --> 00:36:50,200
Thank you.

499
00:36:55,280 --> 00:36:57,360
Pon, Mr. Japan is waiting for you.

500
00:36:57,360 --> 00:36:58,680
Sure.

501
00:36:59,800 --> 00:37:01,120
Pai.

502
00:37:01,560 --> 00:37:02,200
Yes?

503
00:37:02,200 --> 00:37:03,920
