Pupaa.

684
00:46:59,520 --> 00:47:00,920
Let’s go have lunch.

685
00:47:01,360 --> 00:47:02,920
You can come back and do it later.

686
00:47:02,920 --> 00:47:03,720
No, thanks.

687
00:47:03,720 --> 00:47:06,440
I could possibly calculate
a couple of equations while you’re gone.

688
00:47:07,480 --> 00:47:08,520
What are you doing?

689
00:47:09,840 --> 00:47:11,920
Oh, alright.

690
00:47:12,320 --> 00:47:14,160
Do you want me to get you anything?

691
00:47:14,800 --> 00:47:17,080
No, thanks. I’ve prepared my own snack.

692
00:47:17,840 --> 00:47:19,280
Okay.

693
00:47:20,560 --> 00:47:21,600
Work hard.

